<HEADLINE> International Symposium on Antarctic Glaciology Opens in Lanzhou </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LANZHOU, September 5 (Xinhua) -- The Sixth International
Symposium on Antarctic Glaciology opened today in this capital of
northwest China's Gansu Province.
</P>
<P>
Nearly 100 scholars and experts from 19 countries are attending
the symposium at which 110 papers were presented on the research
developments over the past five years.
</P>
