<TEXT>
<P>
Wang, who plays a left-handed topspin game in the handshake
grip, overpowered Sun in the first two sets 21-12, 21-12. But the
18-year-old Sun, who had beat Wang in the Japanese Grand Prix
early this year, fought back to level the score at 8-8 in the
third.
</P>
<P>
The 20-year-old Wang, world silver medallist and World Cup
winner, used her stunning speed and spin to go ahead 20-17 for
