afford to pay it especially in a crisis situation like now. we
will ask for a dispensation."
</P>
<P>
The fine, approved by the ASEAN Football Federation, was
imposed by the Vietnam Football Federation(VFF) tournament
committee following a Tiger Cup final group match between
Thailand and Indonesia on Monday in Ho Chi Minh City, when
neither team played to win to avoid playing host Vietnam in the
semi-finals in Hanoi.
