fined last year for 50,000 dollars after riots erupted during a
final football match for the 19th Southeast Asian Games here.
</P>
<P>
Pembaruan said if its team wins third place, it will win prize
money of 30,000 dollars, leaving it with 10,000 dollars to pay.
